    IntSet, Memento<ThreadInfoSet>, ThreadInfoSet, Cloneable

    public class TidSet
extends UnsortedArrayIntSet
implements ThreadInfoSet, Memento<ThreadInfoSet>
    set that stores threads via (search global) thread ids. Used to detect shared objects/classes, created by configured SharedObjectPolicy factory

        note that there is no guarantee the restored object will be the same that is (optionally) passed in. Implementations are free to restore in-situ or create a new object if a non-null reference is provided.
